data.description: Discover your dream home nestled on a tranquil cul-de-sac in the Kingswood subdivision, surrounded by picturesque woods powered by solar panels that provide the electrical needs of the house and provides dividends from the sale of excess electricity produced - the sellers will assist in paying them off at settlement. This magnificent 5-bedroom , 3.5-bathroom (featuring 1 bedroom & 1 full bathroom on the main floor) residence boasts an impressive array of features. Enjoy the beauty of nature from the comfort of your own backyard from the comfort your own personal spa, with extensive hardscaping, including fruit trees that enhances your outdoor living space.  Entertain family and friends in your private furnished den and movie theater, create culinary delights in the updated kitchen featuring cabinet lighting. With a 2-car garage, solar panel power, and a finished basement, this home offers convenience and energy efficiency.  Experience luxurious comfort with all-new carpet (in carpeted areas) on the main and upper levels, complemented by fresh paint throughout. Welcome to a haven of modern living and timeless elegance.
